 upper boundary on the initial orbital distance where\nsuper-solar metallicity planets are formed. We show that planetesimals are the\nmain source for reaching super-solar metallicity planets. On the other hand,\nplanets that mainly accrete dust grains will show a more solar composition.\nSuper-solar metallicity planets that initiate their formation farther than the\nCO ice line have a C/O ratio closer to the solar value.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Oct 2021 16:15:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-23"}
