 the recent\nmodel of a system of nonrelativistic neutral gravitating particles providing an\nalternative explanation of the entire dynamics of the Universe expansion.\nwithout introducing dark energy or new gravitational degrees of freedom.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Oct 2021 23:30:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-02"}
